=====================================================================
Floe. Instructions

Usage: ./floe <command> <options>

Run ./floe with no arguments to start an interactive shell prompt.

Commands:

# help      - you're looking at it (shortcut <h>)
# project   - create a project (shortcut <p>)
# tasks     - view available tasks (shortcuts <t>, <ls>)
# quit      - quit out of the shell (shortcut <q>)


Skating on thin ice.
